### Key Learnings
- agent coordinates are per-agent relative (can't share WorldModel)
- team_summary.members only counts visible teammates (must default to 8)
- Gear station contention causes 0-score wipeouts if not staggered
- 6 aligners with 2 miners is too thin economically — 5+3 is better
- Score ~2.0 avg with 5 aligners; to get >10 needs fundamental changes
- Hub proximity bias reduces ship damage but doesn't eliminate it
